subject: Olympic Games (2012)
Horsemanship and Equestrian Events
Horses
lead_paragraph: Jan Ebeling rode Rafalca, the horse co-owned by Mitt Romney’s wife, Ann, in the Grand Prix Special portion of the Olympic dressage finals but did not qualify for the Grand Prix Freestyle.
